{
    "name": "Noble Crusader",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat </b>The cleric casts <i>magic vestment</i>.<br/><b>During Combat </b>The cleric attacks with her longsword, and casts <i>magic weapon </i>or <i>align weapon </i>as needed. When fighting undead, she channels positive energy. Otherwise, she uses ranged magical attacks only as a last resort.<br/><b>Base Statistics </b>Without <i>magic vestment</i>, the cleric\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>18, touch 9, flat-footed 18."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "The noble crusader battles the forces of chaos, usually at the behest of a local monarch."
        }
    ],
